    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>REAR SENSOR</title>
        <para>Install the sensor into retainer and sensor mounting block from the axle side in a horizontal position
            with the "cable end" of the sensor positioned as shown in
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0402860">Rear Sensor Figure</hotlnk>, depending on suspension type. Push the sensor into
            the retainer as far as possible. The retainer is located in the sensor mounting block. No further adjustment
            is necessary.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0402860" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g0402860" filename="../figg04/G0402860.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 60. Rear Sensor</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
